      "content": "```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"toolu_01V8LAt5Xh9EHyR9tXeQ4yJS\",\n  \"name\": \"filesystem\",\n  \"content\": \"\\\"\\\"\\\"Base class for AI backends.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, asdict\\nfrom typing import Dict\\n\\n\\n@dataclass\\nclass AIUsage:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Token usage information from AI responses.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    prompt_tokens: int\\n    completion_tokens: int\\n    total_tokens: int\\n    cache_write_tokens: int = 0\\n    cache_read_tokens: int = 0\\n\\n    def to_dict(self) -> Dict:\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"Convert usage to dictionary.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        return asdict(self)\\n\\n    def copy(self) -> 'AIUsage':\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"Create a deep copy of the usage.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n        return AIUsage(\\n            prompt_tokens=self.prompt_tokens,\\n            completion_tokens=self.completion_tokens,\\n            total_tokens=self.total_tokens,\\n            cache_write_tokens=self.cache_write_tokens,\\n            cache_read_tokens=self.cache_read_tokens,\\n        )\\n\",\n  \"error\": null\n}\n```\n`content` is:\n```python\n\"\"\"Base class for AI backends.\"\"\"\n\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, asdict\nfrom typing import Dict\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass AIUsage:\n    \"\"\"Token usage information from AI responses.\"\"\"\n    prompt_tokens: int\n    completion_tokens: int\n    total_tokens: int\n    cache_write_tokens: int = 0\n    cache_read_tokens: int = 0\n\n    def to_dict(self) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"Convert usage to dictionary.\"\"\"\n        return asdict(self)\n\n    def copy(self) -> 'AIUsage':\n        \"\"\"Create a deep copy of the usage.\"\"\"\n        return AIUsage(\n            prompt_tokens=self.prompt_tokens,\n            completion_tokens=self.completion_tokens,\n            total_tokens=self.total_tokens,\n            cache_write_tokens=self.cache_write_tokens,\n            cache_read_tokens=self.cache_read_tokens,\n        )\n\n```",
